Story
The player is an apprentice to a gearsmith named Mard who sends them on a shopping trip to pick up some food for themselves giving 50 federal credits to the apprentice for his food.
They meet several long time acquaintances along the way that the character has known for a long time.
They succesfully grab some food and begin the return trip, after which a masssive groan in the earth sounds.
The groan is coming from a huge burrowing monster that is going to surface three seconds after they hear it. The groans get louder and louder until the ground erupts in a massive storm of dirt and rocks, and the character gets hit 
